Author: Ignacio Vera <ignacio.vera@elastic.co>
Date:   Mon Jan 13 18:54:08 2025 +0100

    Improve error handling when parsing retrievers (#120047) (#120067)
    
    PARSER#declareNamedObject does not handle empty objects or objects with extra stuff.
    Therefore we do it manually.

